Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你小子到底把學校當什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你簡直是私立名門學校朱雀高中建校以來的第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天遲到早退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到處惹是生非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有上課竟然打盹開小差！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師 學級日記我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學啊 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這小子也給我學學白石麗同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遵守紀律 成績優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你是天差地別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切 心高氣傲討人厭的無聊傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 再有下次給我做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是誰啊 眼神好凶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就那個人啊 二年級的問題兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真無聊 虧得我還特意進了沒有熟人的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣和中學時有什麼分別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為有更有意思的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個教科書般的優等生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是保健室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…怎麼變成那傢伙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.23,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)\pos(382,581)}{\pos(273,577)}{\blur3.5}第 1 話  『靈魂交換!』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 那傢伙在我的身體裡面麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 在這種狀態下回到教室什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田那傢伙 發生什麼事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是那麼認真的人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師 這個條件下 a和c可以交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話 把這裡的x帶入a 括弧x的平方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼！跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼我會和你交換了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…你說什麼啊 居然還那麼淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道現在是什麼狀況麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大體上知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大體上是什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於為什麼會發生這種事 我並不知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 復原的方法我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不管怎麼想發生這種事的起因是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩個人在樓梯處摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以只要讓相同的事再發生一遍不就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然連這種事也不知道 真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙性格真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 既然這樣我們馬上去樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為又要暈倒耽誤時間 我不能再翹課了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那你打算你一輩子都這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為股間有個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等到放學後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你在樓梯摔倒了才弄成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這點程度的條件請你認了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算這樣還是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你讓我怎麼用這個身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 這不是絕好的機會麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白……白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起來要倒的樣子 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是…是…是病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好 此時還是應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之我先走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的白石同學 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想趕快變回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 發現白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹嘛啊 我們可是好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佐佐木 凜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帶了白石的便當來 一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡應該適當配合一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 也是 我們去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖說是那傢伙的便當 吃了也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好…好厲害 這就是優等生的便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味道挺不錯誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預習一下下一節課的內容比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優等生的注解真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女人的世界真是骯髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來現在馬上復原比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想讓你也留下不愉快的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們就按照約定好的 放學後再復原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想翹課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等復原後 我一定會讓她們永遠不能再對你出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能不要開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你多管閒事只會讓我困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣只會令事態惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在屋頂上跟山田說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就盡情地拉攏山田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個學校的垃圾 渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果那傢伙對身為女人的我出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後果你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你突然想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今你該不會打算反抗我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我會輕易放過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種傢伙給她一記的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上就會變老實的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟敢打我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是因為你擅自摻和進來我才會打偏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是說好什麼也不做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 今天真是糟糕的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 恢復原狀的話真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙不會再對你出手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在佐佐木同學逃走之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得她真是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙意外的是個坦誠的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們平安地回到了各自地身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本應如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒…沒能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託了 讓我們回到自己的身體裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難不成我們一輩子也變不回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有一個方法我們還沒有試過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們 從樓梯上摔下來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 我為什麼會和你親到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 撲上來的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}試…試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正我們現在這樣也是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧 變回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還要學習 告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是敗給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要親了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然我們的身體又互換了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這件事就作為我們倆個的秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說為什麼這傢伙能這麼冷靜地和我接吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我喜歡山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我們能互換身體的秘密洩露了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過能互換身體真是方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個能用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是學生會的宮村君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然有點凶但是好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能稍微跟我來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是答應今天要和我約會的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那女人有說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭啊 人家才沒有忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近 你和山田關係很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並沒有很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢 優等生的你和不良少年山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本不可能有任何交集呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你這話是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這幾頭蒜是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是你臉色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的什麼事都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用和我客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切交給我們就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石 這裡就交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有這傢伙出頭真是方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宮村 你也太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然 白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學 白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說你們很煩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明只是想和你說說話而已的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對不會再替人做這種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}替人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個迴旋踢 我認得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宮村？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我根本沒有和白石說好要約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這下我就能肯定了 你就是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼啊 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎麼可能是山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你來了啊 白石麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…這個是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事情到了這個地步就沒必要隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 能和我走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟過來一看 山田同學不在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還把秘密讓宮村同學知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用道歉 要不要聽聽我的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}提案？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 我把這個房間讓你們使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們用？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種事還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在的你們在學校需要一個互換的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此 是接吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是接吻互換是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這個人是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觀察力也太強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽人把話說完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡原本就是超常現象研究部使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是部員只有我一個 馬上就要廢部了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你們成為部員的話 就可以自由使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖說是自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是還是有一個問題需要搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田和白石 至今為止有沒有和其他人接過吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要問這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呢 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和白石 是初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雙方都是初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣就有可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 只要和誰接吻就能和那個人互換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學 和我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個我絕對不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就和山田來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是備胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且兩個男的接吻 怎麼可能行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我對這個有些興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請一定讓我見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這曖昧的氛圍是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的換了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害 這就是山田的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的股間果然有個很奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然有個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要一直說這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害 難道說你只要和人接吻就能和那個人互換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了試驗 我現在就去找個能和山田接吻的女生來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請你不要做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石這傢伙 為什麼要反對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我無法原諒山田和其他女生接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果這件事被大家知道了 會出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 就當作我們幾個人的秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛 原來是這個原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然這樣 我可以認定白石同學願意加入超研部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 為什麼你這麼想讓我們加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作為給你們提供房間的交換條件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶爾答應學生會的請求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我認為這個交易很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣好嗎 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 社團活動看起來好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要加入就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天開始 超常現象研究部重新結社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}部長是白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}副部長是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田就是普通社員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通社員是個什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超常現象研究部重新開始活動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此 我也想入部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和白石同學接吻是什麼滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種事我怎麼可能記得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下集 山田君與七魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了 再次和我…
